5
00:00:38,450 --> 00:00:39,618
Bring me the laptop.

6
00:00:54,799 --> 00:00:57,010
You think I can't find you, right?

7
00:00:59,971 --> 00:01:00,931
PROFESSOR KANG JU-MAN

8
00:01:25,372 --> 00:01:26,706
I thought I made it clear.

9
00:01:27,874 --> 00:01:30,252
You aren't allowed
to use a laptop in my class.

10
00:01:30,335 --> 00:01:31,336
Professor.

11
00:01:31,962 --> 00:01:34,422
A student's right
to use a laptop in class is

12
00:01:34,506 --> 00:01:36,174
a matter of self-determination

13
00:01:36,258 --> 00:01:37,968
as guaranteed by the Constitution.

14
00:01:38,051 --> 00:01:39,135
And?

15
00:01:39,219 --> 00:01:42,472
I don't want Article 10,
the right to pursue happiness, infringed

16
00:01:43,056 --> 00:01:44,766
during the Constitution lecture.

17
00:01:44,850 --> 00:01:45,767
Don't you think

18
00:01:46,393 --> 00:01:49,896
what you just said infringes
my right to hold classes as the professor?

19
00:01:50,438 --> 00:01:51,773
This is my court,

20
00:01:51,857 --> 00:01:54,693
and I have a right to teach however I like
when I'm in my turf.

21
00:01:56,236 --> 00:01:58,446
Don't you think you're abusing your right?

22
00:01:58,530 --> 00:02:00,782
It's your dereliction of duty
as a student!

23
00:02:01,658 --> 00:02:02,993
I'll have points deducted.

24
00:02:07,455 --> 00:02:09,833
Do you believe others
didn't bring their laptops

25
00:02:09,916 --> 00:02:11,251
just because of their grades?

26
00:02:11,334 --> 00:02:13,295
I don't know what others are thinking.

27
00:02:13,378 --> 00:02:16,256
I weighed the pros and cons
of using a laptop during this class,

28
00:02:16,339 --> 00:02:18,633
and decided having it here
benefits me more.

29
00:02:18,717 --> 00:02:20,218
Then was this on your list?

30
00:02:21,344 --> 00:02:24,556
The fatal fact that you will be remembered
as the worst student

31
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:25,849
I ever had in my career.

32
00:02:40,238 --> 00:02:41,323
Yes, Professor Kang.

33
00:02:41,406 --> 00:02:44,534
Did you tell Kang Sol B to pick up
her laptop at my office?

34
00:02:44,618 --> 00:02:46,411
She hasn't come for it yet?

35
00:02:46,494 --> 00:02:48,038
I clearly remember telling her.

36
00:02:48,788 --> 00:02:50,332
YANG JONG-HOON
TRASH

37
00:02:52,459 --> 00:02:53,752
Professor?

38
00:02:53,835 --> 00:02:56,588
Are you sure this laptop
is Kang Sol B's laptop?

39
00:02:56,671 --> 00:02:58,840
Yes, I almost had to take it from her
by force.

40
00:02:58,924 --> 00:03:01,760
PROFESSOR KANG JU-MAN

